          With Litecoin being a fairly new technology for money transactions, the technology has spawned positive and negative reviews. 
          Though recently created, the Litecoin community has been very supportive and the new rush of developing applications to support the initial platform for peer to peer transfers is in action. 
          The purpose of this project is to develop a mobile application to help locate and notify users about Litecoin & Bitcoin ATM and business locations. 
          This application will decrease the time needed to find Litecoin & Bitcoin extraction points for Litecoin & Bitcoin holders around the globe. SpotLite primarily focuses on Asia and Europe. 
          Our goal is to simplify the experience of where to spend Litecoin & Bitcoin in the area surrounding the user, using location based services and alerts. 
